tmobile_center.note: The T-Mobile Center offers a variety of food and drink options, including traditional stadium fare and specialty items. Highlights include gourmet burgers, craft beers, and a selection of local favorites. Special offerings may include themed food items for specific events.

tmobile_park.note: T-Mobile Park offers a diverse range of food and drink options, from local favorites like Moto Pizza and Ivar's to classic ballpark snacks. Highlights include the Nakagawa Poke Bowl, Ivar's Halibut and Chips, and Casamigos Cocktails available throughout the concourse. Special offerings include the Ichi Wings and Turn Two Teriyaki Chicken Bowl.

talking_stick_resort_amphitheatre.note: Talking Stick Resort Amphitheatre offers a variety of food and drink options, including Mosh Burger's hormone-free beef burgers, Rebel Hen's crispy chicken tenders, and Ziggy's Magic Pizza Party's NY-inspired pizza. Guests can also enjoy Koko's Bavarian sausages and pretzels, as well as CVT Premium Soft Serve Ice Cream.

tottenham_hotspur_stadium.note: Tottenham Hotspur Stadium offers a variety of food and drink options, including hot food, salads, barista coffee, and bakery goods at the M Café, which is open daily except on event days. Special event menus and exclusive items like loaded nachos and doughnuts are available during specific events.

toyota_center.note: The Toyota Center offers a variety of food and drink options, including traditional stadium fare and specialty items. Highlights include local favorites and unique culinary offerings. Special offerings may include themed food nights or exclusive vendor partnerships.

truist_park.note: Truist Park offers a variety of food and beverage options, including classic comfort foods with bold flavors and modern twists. Highlights include the Beer Garden for local brews, Bridges Grille's signature Garlic Fries, and Cadillac Diner's indulgent Chili Cheese Hot Dog. New offerings include a Bacon Wrapped Hot Dog and Pastrami Fry.

ubc_doug_mitchell_thunderbird_sports_cen.note: The Doug Mitchell Thunderbird Sports Centre offers a variety of food choices, including healthy options, at its concession stands. Beverages are also available for every event, ensuring guests can quickly return to their seats.

ubs_arena.note: UBS Arena offers a diverse range of dining options with 12 market-style outlets featuring hot, freshly prepared foods, ready-to-go meals, and self-serve snacks and beverages. Highlights include vegetarian, gluten-free, and kosher options, as well as unique offerings like the 'Fear the Schmear' Porkbelly and Habanero Sandwich and Benihana Hibachi Bowls.

uc_berkeley_greek_theatre.note: The Greek Theatre offers a variety of food concessions throughout the venue, featuring an array of snacks and specialty drinks. Visitors can enjoy a wide selection of refreshments during events.

us_bank_stadium.note: U.S. Bank Stadium offers a diverse range of food and beverage options, including local Minnesota flavors. Highlights include bratwurst, cheeseburgers, cheese curds, and a variety of snacks like popcorn and nachos. Beverage options feature craft beers and cocktails.

unipol_arena.note: Food and drinks are heavily restricted inside the arena. Only plastic bottles up to 0.5 liters without caps are allowed, and bringing in any kind of food is prohibited unless exceptions are made by contacting the venue.

unipol_forum.note: Inside the Unipol Forum, visitors can enjoy a variety of food and drink options, including several bars and a large food court. Specific details about the offerings are not provided.

unity_arena.note: The Food Court at Aker Tech House offers a diverse selection of cuisines from around the world, prepared in an open kitchen with live flames. It serves as a lunch destination for both locals and visitors, featuring flavorful dishes from four unique cuisines.

utah_first_credit_union_amphitheatre.note: Utah First Credit Union Amphitheatre offers a variety of food and drink options, including Mosh Burger's hormone-free beef burgers, Rebel Hen's crispy chicken tenders, and Ziggy's Magic Pizza Shop's NY-inspired pizzas. Koko's Bavarian provides German-inspired sausages and pretzels, while general concessions offer popcorn, nachos, and a selection of beverages. CVT Premium Soft Serve Ice Cream is also available in a convenient pouch.
stands: CVT Premium Soft Serve Ice Cream

utilita_arena_birmingham.note: Utilita Arena Birmingham offers a range of food and drink options, including pre-show dining and interval drinks in their Premium lounges. Visitors can enjoy a variety of bites and beverages without missing any of the action.

utilita_arena_sheffield.note: Utilita Arena Sheffield offers a variety of food and drink options with a focus on fresh, tasty, and locally sourced products. Gluten-free and vegan options are available, and all outlets are cashless, accepting only card payments.

uw_panther_arena.note: UW-Milwaukee Panther Arena offers a diverse range of food and beverage options through its partner, Levy Restaurants. The menu includes quality concessions, backstage catering, and elegant banquet options, with dietary accommodations noted for gluten-free, nut, seafood, vegan, and vegetarian preferences.

van_andel_arena.note: Van Andel Arena offers a variety of food and beverage options through its exclusive partner, Legends Global. The venue emphasizes local flavors and cashless transactions, with gift cards available for purchase. Alcohol purchases require ID validation.

veterans_memorial_coliseum.note: Veterans Memorial Coliseum offers a variety of food and drink options including local favorites like 19 Acres Cider and Cha Cha Cha. Visitors can enjoy a range of offerings from BBQ and Mexican food to vegan and vegetarian options. Special highlights include the woman-owned Fusion Shave Ice stand.

veterans_united_home_loans_amphitheater.note: Veterans United Home Loans Amphitheater offers a variety of food and drink options, including Mosh Burger's hormone-free beef burgers, Rebel Hen's crispy chicken tenders, and Ziggy's Magic Pizza Shop's NY-inspired pizzas. Guests can also enjoy Koko's Bavarian sausages and pretzels, as well as CVT Premium Soft Serve Ice Cream. Concessions include classic concert bites like popcorn and nachos, along with a selection of alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages.
stands: CVT Premium Soft Serve Ice Cream

videotron_centre.note: The Videotron Centre offers a variety of high-quality food concessions with menus to suit all tastes and budgets, including gourmet options in premium areas. Club Bud lounge bar provides a wide selection of Labatt beers in a festive atmosphere.

viejas_arena.note: Viejas Arena offers a variety of food and drink options including bratwurst, hot dogs, nachos, and specialty mac & cheese. Beverage options feature a wide selection of beers, wines, and cocktails, with several third-party vendors providing diverse offerings like pizza, cheesesteaks, and ice cream.

villa_erba.note: The page does not provide specific information about food and drink options or special offerings at Villa Erba.

wamu_theater.note: WAMU Theater offers a variety of food and beverage options including fan favorites like chicken strips with fries, Bavarian pretzels with cheese, and handcrafted cocktails. The venue also features a Starbucks menu with espresso drinks and pastries. Outside food is allowed under specific conditions, but outside beverages are generally not permitted.

wells_fargo_arena.note: Wells Fargo Arena offers a variety of food and drink options, including classic arena fare like hot dogs, nachos, and popcorn, as well as specialty items such as local craft beers and gourmet snacks. The venue occasionally features themed food events and limited-time offerings.

wells_fargo_center.note: Wells Fargo Center offers a wide variety of food and drink options, including popular chains like Shake Shack and Chickie's & Pete's, as well as local favorites such as Federal Donuts and 9th Street Italian Sandwiches. Special offerings include gluten-free options and kosher meals, ensuring there's something for everyone.

wembley_stadium.note: Wembley Stadium offers a variety of food and drink options including hearty and healthy breakfast menus, buffet and bowl food menus, and a la carte dining. Special offerings include customizable day delegate packages and dinner packages with room hire and drinks. The venue also provides options for canape receptions and drinks receptions.

winstar_lucas_oil_live.note: Union Mesa Restaurant & Cantina offers a refined take on traditional Tex-Mex cuisine with a curated menu featuring both classic and innovative dishes. Highlights include top shelf tequila selections, a unique margarita menu, and happy hour specials from 4:00 – 6:00 PM Monday – Wednesday.

wrigley_field.note: Wrigley Field offers a variety of food and beverage options including classic comfort foods with modern twists, such as Chicken Tenders & Fries, Cheeseburgers, and specialty hot dogs. Highlights include the Bacon Wrapped Hot Dog and Pastrami Fry. Fans can also enjoy a selection of local and popular beers at the Beer Garden.

xl_center.note: The XL Center offers a diverse range of food and drink options, including New England Style Barbeque, specialty baked potatoes, and unique pizza flavors like Peanut Butter & Bacon. Visitors can enjoy a variety of beverages from local craft beers to mixed drinks and soft drinks.

xcel_energy_center.note: Xcel Energy Center offers a variety of food and drink options including traditional sausages, craft beers, pizza, burgers, and more. Special offerings include the Wild $6 Happy Hour and the Wild Market with Amazon’s Just Walk Out technology. Alcohol sales end during the third period of Minnesota Wild games or one hour before the end of other events.

yankee_stadium.note: Yankee Stadium offers a variety of food and drink options, including classic comfort foods with bold flavors and modern twists. Highlights include specialty items like Bacon Wrapped Hot Dogs, Pastrami Fries, and indulgent treats like Soft Serve and Milkshakes. The venue features a lively Beer Garden and several concession stands with unique offerings.

stagecoach_festival.note: The Stagecoach Festival in Indio, CA offers a variety of food and drink options, featuring local and international cuisines. Attendees can enjoy a range of culinary delights from food trucks and pop-up restaurants, with special offerings that cater to diverse dietary preferences.

edc_las_vegas.note: EDC Las Vegas offers an exclusive bottle service experience with private table service, a full bottle service menu, and access to private VIP restroom facilities. Guests can enjoy a welcome glass of champagne and golf cart transport to their table.

electric_forest.note: The Electric Forest festival offers a variety of food vendors and artisan shops located in the Main Street GA Campground Hub/Marketplace. Attendees can enjoy tasty treats in the new Uplift Lounge, exclusive to pass holders.

bonnaroo_music_arts_festival.note: The Bonnaroo Music & Arts Festival offers a variety of food and drink options, featuring partnerships with popular brands like Coke, Jack Daniel's, and White Claw. Attendees can enjoy a diverse selection of beverages and culinary experiences throughout the festival grounds.

governors_ball.note: The Governors Ball features a variety of food options from familiar New York restaurants and vendors, including some from the Queens Night Market. The festival offers five food courts for general admission ticket holders, ensuring a diverse culinary experience.

boston_calling.note: The document does not provide specific details about food and drink options at Boston Calling. Typically, such events feature a variety of local food vendors and beverage options, including craft beers and specialty cocktails.

bottlerock_napa_valley.note: BottleRock Napa Valley offers a diverse range of food and drink options, featuring local and renowned chefs, restaurants, and wineries. Attendees can enjoy gourmet dishes, artisanal snacks, and a variety of beverages, including craft beers and fine wines. The festival is known for its culinary stage where celebrity chefs and musicians collaborate for unique cooking demonstrations.

hangout_music_festival.note: The Hangout Music Festival offers a variety of food and drink options, including dozens of restaurants and the Hangout Restaurant for a shaded, air-conditioned meal. The Nosh Pit provides snacks all day long in a new shaded dining pavilion.

lollapalooza.note: The Chicago Park District offers a variety of concessionaires providing unique dining and recreational opportunities. These include sit-down meals, quick snacks, and rental services. Concessions typically operate from Memorial Day weekend through Labor Day.

rolling_loud_miami.note: Hard Rock Stadium offers a diverse range of food options including American, Tex-Mex, Japanese, and Cuban cuisines. Highlights include mobile ordering at select locations and a cashless payment system. Unique offerings include hibachi from Benihana and upscale options at Seafood Republic.

rolling_loud_los_angeles.note: Hollywood Park offers a diverse range of food and drink options with 99 food and retail brands. Visitors can enjoy lakefront dining, cocktails, and a vibrant open-air celebration of Los Angeles culture.

summerfest.note: Summerfest 2025 introduces a diverse array of new food and beverage options, including unique items like Lumpia City Mac 'n Cheese Rolls and Funnel Cake Pork Sandwiches. The festival also highlights local vendors through the BMO Small Business Spotlight program.
stands: Select American Family Insurance Amphitheater Concession Areas

new_orleans_jazz_heritage_festival.note: The New Orleans Jazz & Heritage Festival offers a diverse array of food options, including BBQ, seafood, and vegan dishes. Highlights include the Whiskey Bacon & Swiss Burger, Crawfish Mac & Cheese, and Chargrilled Oysters. Unique offerings such as the Surf ‘n Turf Pupusa and Ropa Vieja Modelo Queso Mac showcase the festival's culinary creativity.

austin_city_limits_music_festival.note: The venue is cashless, and all concessions, bars, and merchandise stands accept credit/debit cards and mobile payments only. No specific food or drink options are detailed on the page.

when_we_were_young.note: The venue offers a variety of quick-serve food and drink options, including gourmet coffees and pastries at Starbucks, fresh doughnuts at Krispy Kreme, and Italian gelato at Cocolini. Guests can also enjoy classic fast-food offerings from Popeyes and Dairy Queen, as well as Asian cuisine from Pick Up Stix.

life_is_beautiful.note: Life is Beautiful 2023 offers a diverse range of food and drink options, including a curated Pizzeria with rotating menus from top pizzaiolos and an Omakase Cantina featuring high-concept dinners. Attendees can enjoy offerings from popular Las Vegas restaurants and vendors throughout the festival.

music_midtown.note: Piedmont Park offers a variety of food and beverage options through its concessions, including hot snacks and cold drinks. Notable vendors include Henri’s Bakery & Deli, Shake Shack, Willy’s Mexicana Grill, and Howlin Willy’s, providing diverse dining choices for visitors.

hard_summer_music_festival.note: The venue offers a vibrant selection of food and drink options, featuring 99 food and retail brands. Visitors can enjoy lakefront dining and cocktails, along with a variety of local favorites and star-powered retailers.

country_thunder_wisconsin.note: The venue offers a full-service bar and daily appetizers as part of the Platinum Experience. VIP catering options are available for private skyboxes, and catered meals are provided with Premier Camping packages.

electric_zoo.note: The Brew at the Zoo event at Central Park Zoo features a variety of breweries and food vendors. Attendees can expect a diverse selection of food and drink options. Check back soon for more additions.

riot_fest.note: The Taste of River North event features a diverse selection of food options from popular local restaurants. Highlights include offerings from Lure Fishbar, Moe's Cantina, and Fogo De Chao, among others.

essence_festival_of_culture.note: The venue features Dutch’s Corner, an in-house convenience store located next to the UPS Store in Lobby E. It offers a variety of snacks and beverages for attendees.

sxsw_music_film_interactive.note: The SXSW event offers a variety of food and drink options, including local Austin favorites and international cuisine. Attendees can enjoy a mix of traditional and innovative food offerings, with special emphasis on sustainability and local sourcing.

cma_fest.note: The CMA Fest in Nashville offers a variety of food and drink options, featuring local and regional cuisine. Attendees can enjoy a range of culinary delights from numerous vendors, with special offerings that highlight the vibrant food scene of Nashville.

made_in_america.note: The National Constitution Center offers a variety of food and beverage options including Delegates' Cafe and Starbucks. Delegates' Cafe features salads, sandwiches, and daily specials like Philly cheesesteaks, while Starbucks provides handcrafted beverages and premium teas. Catering and boxed lunch options are available for groups.

radio_city_music_hall.note: Radio City Music Hall offers a variety of food and drink options, including classic concessions and specialty items. Guests can enjoy a range of snacks and beverages, with highlights such as gourmet hot dogs and artisanal cocktails. The venue also features unique offerings tailored to enhance the event experience.

the_gorge_amphitheatre.note: The Gorge Amphitheatre offers a variety of food and drink options, including Mosh Burger's hormone-free beef burgers, Rebel Hen's crispy chicken tenders, and Ziggy's Magic Pizza Shop's NY-inspired pizzas. Koko's Bavarian provides German-inspired sausages and pretzels, while general concessions offer popcorn, nachos, and a selection of beverages.
